<note n="0607005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607005">經＝紺ヵ【原】</note>
<note n="0607006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607006">面＋（有吽字變成）ヵ【原】</note>
<note n="0607007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607007">〔像畫〕－ヵ【原】</note>
<note n="0607008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607008">牟＋（一）ィ細註【原】</note>
<note n="0607009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607009">全＝余ィ【原】</note>
<note n="0607010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0607010">唎＋（五）ィ細註【原】</note>
